<section id="about">
<h2>About the Breed</h2>
<p>
The English Bulldog is one of the most recognizable dog breeds in the world. Known for their wrinkled face,
stocky body, and lovable personality, bulldogs are loyal companions and excellent family pets.
</p>
<p>
Despite their tough appearance, they are gentle, affectionate, and love spending time with their owners.
</p>
</section>

<section id="care">
<h2>Bulldog Care</h2>
<ul>
<li>Daily short walks</li>
<li>Regular cleaning of facial wrinkles</li>
<li>Moderate exercise (they overheat easily)</li>
<li>High-quality dog food</li>
<li>Routine vet visits</li>
</ul>
